[Date: Wed, 11 Jan 2023 00:59:56 +0000 (UTC) From: Patients Know Best To: cy_cz.patient.1@pkbtest.com Message-ID: <691251482.1507.1673398796300@26072c911b4a> Subject: Mr AZ Patient 3 would like to share their health record with you MIME-Version: 1.0 Content-Type: multipart/mixed; boundary="----=_Part_1504_2009831708.1673398796297" ------=_Part_1504_2009831708.1673398796297 Content-Type: multipart/related; boundary="----=_Part_1505_1694541125.1673398796297" ------=_Part_1505_1694541125.1673398796297 Content-Type: multipart/alternative; boundary="----=_Part_1506_1335408664.1673398796297" ------=_Part_1506_1335408664.1673398796297 Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8 Content-Transfer-Encoding: 7bit Dear Mr CyCz Patient 1, Mr AZ Patient 3 has invited you to access their medical information so you can help manage their health. ---------- Message from Mr AZ Patient 3 Add carer ---------- To accept this invitation, click this link: http://pkb-frontend-5/patient/accept.action?invitationId=422a38b2-2404-48f3-942c-62e1c9535c3c&e=cy_cz.patient.1@pkbtest.com You are receiving this notification because you are a carer.
